###  https://example.org/story/social#allyOf
<https://example.org/story/social#allyOf> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                          rdfs:subPropertyOf <https://example.org/story/social#sociallyRelatedTo> ;
                                          rdf:type owl:SymmetricProperty ,
                                                   owl:IrreflexiveProperty ;
                                          owl:propertyDisjointWith <https://example.org/story/social#hated> ;
                                          rdfs:comment "Alliance, cooperating towards a common goal. Not necessarily friends."@en ;
                                          rdfs:label "ally of"@en .


###  https://example.org/story/social#companionOf
