                                                rdf:type owl:AsymmetricProperty ,
                                                         owl:IrreflexiveProperty ;
                                                rdfs:comment "Raising someone as a foster-child. E.g. Thingol fosters Túrin."@en ;
                                                rdfs:label "fosters child"@en .


###  https://example.org/story/social#friendOf
<https://example.org/story/social#friendOf> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
