                                                                     <https://example.org/story/social#serves> ;
                                            rdfs:comment "Friendship between two characters."@en ;
                                            rdfs:label "friend of"@en .


###  https://example.org/story/social#hasBearer
<https://example.org/story/social#hasBearer> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ,
                                                      owl:IrreflexiveProperty .


###  https://example.org/story/social#hasBeloved
