                                                                            <https://example.org/story/social#hasKnownCharacter>
                                                                          ) ;
                                                   rdfs:comment "A knower identifies or recognizes a character. Inferred from an IdentityKnowledgeState."@en ;
                                                   rdfs:label "knows identity of"@en .


###  https://example.org/story/social#livedIn
