                                                                        <https://example.org/story/time#startedByInterval> ,
                                                                        <https://example.org/story/time#startsInterval> ;
                                               rdfs:comment "Allen's 'meets': first interval ends exactly when second starts. Asymmetric (if I meets J, then J does not meet I) and irreflexive (an interval cannot meet itself)."@en ;
                                               rdfs:label "meets"@en .


###  https://example.org/story/time#metByInterval
